227
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:44,680
Bože, láme mi srdce.

228
00:24:44,680 --> 00:24:46,400
<i>Je niekto doma?</i>

229
00:24:47,280 --> 00:24:48,880
Kto to je?

230
00:25:01,560 --> 00:25:04,840
