až na golfové ihrisko.

297
00:30:47,600 --> 00:30:50,240
Nikto tomu neveril.

298
00:30:50,240 --> 00:30:51,000
Naozaj?

299
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:54,360
Áno. Moja dcéra je naozaj obdarená

300
00:30:54,360 --> 00:30:58,160
