342
00:33:56,560 --> 00:33:59,040
Ja golf hrať neviem.

343
00:33:59,040 --> 00:34:02,760
Pre nosičov to je zdarma?

344
00:34:02,760 --> 00:34:05,920
Áno. Prečo?

345
00:34:07,880 --> 00:34:09,719
Náhodou, ty...

346
00:34:09,719 --> 00:34:12,679
Nie, nič, len tak.

347
00:34:12,679 --> 00:34:15,239
Keď je to pre nosičov zdarma...

348
00:34:15,239 --> 00:34:17,480
Ty, ty!

349
00:34:17,719 --> 00:34:19,520
Nemyslím to tak.

350
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:42,800
Dlho sme sa nevideli.

351
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:49,440
