381
00:37:21,200 --> 00:37:26,520
Mi Soo. Min Hae Ryungin tréner...

382
00:37:26,520 --> 00:37:28,520
Poznáš ho, že?

383
00:37:28,520 --> 00:37:31,000
Tréner? John Lee?

